Package org.bukkit

Interface Registry<T extends Keyed>

Type Parameters:
T - type of item in the registry
All Superinterfaces:
Iterable<T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
Registry.SimpleRegistry
public interface Registry<T extends Keyed>
extends Iterable<T>
Represents a registry of Bukkit objects that may be retrieved by NamespacedKey.
